devdoc.details: ERC-721 compliant token representing unique Mememonize assets. This contract includes marketplace functionality for listing and purchasing NFTs.

constructor.details: Initializes the contract by setting a name and a symbol for the NFT.

params.price: The sale price in wei for which the NFT will be listed.
params.recipient: The address that will own the minted NFT.
params.tokenURI: The token URI that points to the NFT metadata.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.
